# Dashboard Module Implementation

The Dashboard module provides summary statistics and a daily overview for clinic staff.

## Proposed Changes

### Backend Components

#### [NEW] [dashboard.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/backend/src/modules/dashboard/dashboard.service.ts)
- `getStats`: Returns counts for patients, appointments today, and monthly revenue.
- `getDailySchedule`: Returns today's appointments for a quick overview.

#### [NEW] [dashboard.controller.ts](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/backend/src/modules/dashboard/dashboard.controller.ts)
- `getDashboardData`: Main endpoint combining stats and schedule.

#### [NEW] [dashboard.module.ts](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/backend/src/modules/dashboard/dashboard.module.ts)
- Standard NestJS module setup.

